'''飓风阿琳'''（{{lang-en|Hurricane Arlene}}）是[[1963年大西洋飓风季|1963年大西洋飓风季]]的第一个[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]，也是有纪录以来在[[百慕大|百慕大]]产生降水最多的三场风暴之一。气旋于7月31日成为热带低气压，然后经快速增强于8月2日达到现代[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]的二级飓风标准{{#tag:ref|[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]于1971年面世<ref name="USA Today">{{cite news | author = Jack Williams | title = Hurricane scale invented to communicate storm danger | publisher = [[今日美国|USA Today]] | date = 2005-05-17 | accessdate = 2013-08-04 | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/hurricane/whscale.htm | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160324154907/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/hurricane/whscale.htm | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-24 }}</ref>，再对[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]大西洋飓风数据库的所有风暴追溯分级<ref>{{cite report | publisher = Hurricane Research Division | title = Chronological List of All Continental United States Hurricanes: 1851-2012 | date = 2013-06 | accessdate = 2016-11-10 | archivedate = 2016-05-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160503012801/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/All_U.S._Hurricanes.html | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/All_U.S._Hurricanes.html }}</ref>。|group="注"}}。接下来风暴转向西进并快速减弱，到8月4日已消退成热带低气压。此后两天阿琳未能重新组织，直到8月7日才增强成热带风暴。次日，气旋在达到飓风标准后直接从[[百慕大|百慕大]]上空经过。数小时后，阿琳达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]160公里、最低[[气压|气压]]969[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，28.61[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）的最高强度。到了8月11日，风暴已转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]，最终于当天被另一个气旋吸收。

风暴期间，[[背风群岛_(加勒比海)|背风群岛]]收到多份[[热带气旋警告|飓风警告或观察预警]]，但实际上没有任何岛屿遭受破坏。阿琳对百慕大有重大影响，狂风和创纪录的降雨量导致树木倒塌、电缆中断并引发洪灾，全岛损失总额约为30万美元{{#tag:ref|如无特别说明，所有损失数额均为1963年[[美元|美元]]价值。|group="注"}}。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Arlene 1963 track.png}}
7月31日，{{lang|en|[[卫星影像|TIROS VI]]}}型气象卫星发现[[小安的列斯群岛|小安的列斯群岛]]和[[佛得角|佛得角]]之间存在规模庞大的热带低气压，估计直径横跨[[经度|经度]]达到五度<ref name="MWR">{{cite web | author = Gordon E. Dunn | publisher = United States Weather Bureau Office in Miami, Florida | year = 1964 | accessdate = 2017-02-12 | title = The Hurricane Season of 1963 | archivedate = 2017-01-28 | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/1963.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170128012826/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/1963.pdf | deadurl = no | format = PDF }}</ref>。气旋稳步向西移动，然后转向西北，于8月2日增强成热带风暴并获名“阿琳”（{{lang|en|Arlene}}）<ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | author = Hurricane Specialists Division | publisher = National Hurricane Center | year = 2009 | accessdate = 2017-02-12 | title = Easy to Read HURDAT 2008 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305031132/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/easyread-2009.html | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/easyread-2009.html }}</ref>。当晚，[[美国海军|美国海军]]侦察机飞入风暴后发现清晰的[[风眼|风眼]]并测得987[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，29.15[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）[[气压|气压]]，气旋因此升级成飓风<ref name="TCR3">{{cite web | author = Staff Writer | publisher = United States Weather Bureau Office | year = 1964 | accessdate = 2017-02-12 | title = Hurricane Arlene Preliminary Report Page Three | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303211156/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1963/arlene/prenhc/prelim03.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1963/arlene/prenhc/prelim03.gif | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | format = [[GIF|GIF]] }}</ref>，此时距热带低气压形成还只过去18小时，已属[[快速增强|快速增强]]。接下来又经过六小时强化，阿琳的[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]达到155公里，在现代[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下已属二级飓风标准。<ref name="HURDAT" />

8月3日清晨，风暴再度转朝西面移动，并因核心附近的[[风切变|垂直风切变]]突然增长开始减弱<ref name="MWR" /><ref name="TCR3" />，于8月4日降级成热带低气压<ref name="HURDAT" />。当晚，气旋从[[背风群岛_(加勒比海)|背风群岛]]北部附近经过<ref name="HURDAT" />，整体结构杂乱无章<ref name="MWR" />。热带低气压稳步向西北前进，于8月7日开始重新发展<ref name="TCR3" />。

阿琳开始重新组织的同时几乎停止移动，之后又转向东北并加快前进速度，开始回转进入主[[西风带|西风带]]<ref name="TCR3" />。8月8日，气旋附近多艘船只测得烈风强度大风<ref name="MWR" /><ref name="HURDAT" />，气象机构因此恢复公告发布<ref name="TCR3" />。8月8日晚，海军侦察机在风暴中心周围测得飓风强度风力，阿琳由此再度升级成飓风<ref name="MWR" />。

{{在百慕大产生降水最多的热带气旋|align=right}}

8月9日，风暴以持续风速每小时140公里强度直接从[[百慕大|百慕大]]上空经过<ref name="HURDAT" /><ref name="TCR3" />，还在经过该岛后继续增强，侦察机测得969毫巴（百帕，28.61英寸汞柱）气压<ref name="TCR3" />，最大持续风速提高到每小时160公里<ref name="HURDAT" />。飓风于数小时后开始减弱<ref name="MWR" />，风速到8月10日下午已降至每小时不足155公里。不久，仍有飓风强度的阿琳在北大西洋上空转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]<ref name="HURDAT" />，最终于8月11日被[[纽芬兰岛|纽芬兰岛]]附近更大规模的气旋吸收<ref name="MWR" />。

== 防灾措施和影响 ==
8月3日，[[美国国家气象局|美国国家气象局]]驻[[波多黎各|波多黎各]][[圣胡安_(波多黎各)|圣胡安]]办事处向背风群岛北部发布[[热带气旋警告|飓风警告]]，并向[[维尔京群岛|维尔京群岛]]发布飓风观察预警，预警范围之后还延伸到波多黎各<ref name="TCR4">{{cite web | author1 = Davis | author2 = Zimmer | publisher = United States Weather Bureau Office | year = 1964 | accessdate = 2017-02-12 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1963/arlene/prenhc/prelim04.gif | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303223333/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1963/arlene/prenhc/prelim04.gif | title = Hurricane Arlene Preliminary Report Page Four | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | format = GIF }}</ref>。到了8月4日阿琳弱化成热带风暴后，上述飓风警告已降级为烈风警告，飓风观察预警停止生效。气旋当天进一步消退成热带低气压后，所有警告或预警全部中止。<ref name="TCR5">{{cite web | author1 = Hoose | author2 = Higgs | author3 = Davis | publisher = [[美国国家气象局|United States Weather Bureau Office]] | year = 1964 | accessdate = 2017-02-12 | title = Hurricane Arlene Preliminary Report Page Five | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | format = GIF | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303235908/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1963/arlene/prenhc/prelim05.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1963/arlene/prenhc/prelim05.gif }}</ref>8月8口阿琳重新发展后，百慕大居民接获通知，建议他们不要冒险出海并做好应对飓风来袭的准备<ref name="TCR12">{{cite web | author1 = Dunn | author2 = Sugg | author3 = Moore | publisher = United States Weather Bureau Office | year = 1964 | accessdate = 2017-02-12 | title = Hurricane Arlene Preliminary Report Page Twelve | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303193601/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1963/arlene/prenhc/prelim12.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1963/arlene/prenhc/prelim12.gif | deadurl = no | format = GIF }}</ref>。

风暴经过期间，百慕大测得时速140公里的狂风和974.5毫巴（百帕，28.78英寸汞柱）气压<ref name="TCR3" />。[[金德利空军基地|金德利空军基地]]所测阵风时速最高，达158公里<ref name="TCR13">{{cite web | author1 = Moore | author2 = Clark | publisher = United States Weather Bureau Office | year = 1964 | accessdate = 2017-02-12 | title = Hurricane Arlene Preliminary Report Page Thirteen | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | format = GIF | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303165644/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1963/arlene/prenhc/prelim13.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1963/arlene/prenhc/prelim13.gif }}</ref>。岛上各地都有树枝断裂和供电线缆中断，少量小型船只因海况恶劣淹没，部分地点还发生洪灾<ref>{{cite web | agency = [[合众国际社|United Press International]] | newspaper = The Bend Bulletin | date = 1963-08-10 | accessdate = 2017-02-12 | title = Arlene moves out to sea after hitting Bermuda | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=weYSAAAAIBAJ&sjid=8_cDAAAAIBAJ&pg=4390,5655470&dq=hurricane+arlene+bermuda | archive-date = 2021-09-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210929012838/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=weYSAAAAIBAJ&sjid=8_cDAAAAIBAJ&pg=4390%2C5655470&dq=hurricane+arlene+bermuda }}</ref>。阿琳在岛上的降雨量达154毫米，仅次于[[1939年大西洋飓风季#第四号飓风|1939年的第四号飓风]]和[[2016年大西洋飓风季|2016年]]的[[2016年飓风妮科尔|飓风妮科尔]]<ref name="WPCMAX" />。百慕大遭受的破坏总额约为30万美元<ref name="MWR" />。

